Amakam zaitim Chintnam motint adolltat: Borim chintnam va vaitt chintnam

Tujem mon borem asot zalear, tuka borim chintnam motint yetat. Tujem monn khottem asot zalear khottim chintnan va vaitt chintnam motint yetat.

Monxean borem chintlear, saud bori urta ani vaitt chintlear, saud piddear zata.

Borem chintun ami khuxal zaunk xoktat ani vaitt chintlear dukest zaunk xoktat.


